Package: cmake4epics
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: epics-dev
Description: Building EPICS Modules with CMake
 A set of CMake modules that enables developers to build EPICS
 applications like IOCs as well as libraries like device support
 modules using CMake. Cross-builds are supported as well.
